(506, 1, '2020-03-19 11:50:56', '2020-03-19 11:50:56', '<!-- wp:html -->\n[ux_banner height=\"100%\" bg=\"8264\" bg_color=\"rgb(224, 240, 212)\"]\n\n[text_box text_color=\"dark\" width=\"79\" width__sm=\"85\" scale=\"107\" animate=\"fadeInUp\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"15\"]\n\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 170%;\"><strong>JunNG Corner</strong></span></h2>\n<p>As an introvert I refuse to show off, people shouldnâ€™t always have to work so hard to show off the best thing about themselves. I always find it is so contradicting to love something and then have to prove it to people. So this place is simple. Itâ€™s filled with what I love thatâ€™s been stocked up in side my mind. Take a look in side!</p>\n[search]\n\n[button text=\"Click me!\" radius=\"99\" link=\"#MY GALLERY\"]\n\n\n[/text_box]\n[ux_image id=\"421\" depth=\"4\" depth_hover=\"1\" animate=\"fadeInUp\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"95\"]\n\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[section label=\"Simple Light\" bg_color=\"rgb(245, 245, 245)\" padding=\"27px\" border=\"1px 0px 0px 0px\" border_color=\"rgb(235, 235, 235)\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n[featured_box margin=\"px px px px\"]\n\n<h3>Painting</h3>\n<p>Something I did back in highschool, cause who give a shit about colledge. I still went, but doesn\'t mean I can\'t do what I like in highschool</p>\n[ux_gallery ids=\"422,423,424\" style=\"none\" type=\"slider\" col_spacing=\"collapse\" columns=\"2\" depth=\"2\" depth_hover=\"1\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\" image_size=\"thumbnail\"]\n\n\n[/featured_box]\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<h3>Stories board</h3>\n<p>For short stories, mostly homework.</p>\n<p>I did enjoy it. Cause it\'s easy.</p>\n[ux_gallery ids=\"425,426,427,428\" style=\"none\" type=\"slider\" col_spacing=\"collapse\" columns=\"2\" depth=\"2\" depth_hover=\"1\" animate=\"fadeInLeft\" image_size=\"thumbnail\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"12\"]\n\n<h3>Sketch</h3>\n<p>Step into a little bit more professional but not