ver_alt=\"overlay-add\" link=\"#\"]\n\n[text_box width=\"40\" width__sm=\"97\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"uppercase\"><strong>3D</strong></h3>\n<p>Â </p>\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n\n[/col_grid]\n\n[/ux_banner_grid]\n[gap]\n\n[ux_banner height=\"400px\" bg=\"8266\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.49)\" bg_pos=\"26% 17%\"]\n\n[text_box text_color=\"dark\" width=\"93\" width__sm=\"60\" scale=\"59\" position_x=\"50\" position_y=\"50\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"uppercase\"><strong>List your Company</strong></h3>\n<p><img class=\"alignnonewp-image-473\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/JunNg/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Logo-nhoÌm-565x400.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"69\" height=\"49\" /></p>\n<p class=\"p1\">THIEU NU PRODUCTION</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">On the blazing summer day, there was a cicada lazily lying around under healthy green foliage, holds on to its musical instrument and sings all day long. The cicada suddenly sees an ant that is struggling to carry a huge grain of rice and slowly passing by. Leisurely, the cicada said:</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">â€œHey ant, on such a sunny day like this, why donâ€™t you take a break? Why must you exhaust yourself like that.â€</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">Heard what the cicada said, the ant raised his head slightly, as he wiped away the sweat he responds. â€œOh Cicada? Of course I want to take a break, but winter will come. If I don\'t worry about food storage now, I don\'t know how my kids will live in the winter. â€</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">â€œHa ha, oh dear ant, your worries are still too far away. There are still summer and autumn and after that it will be winter. Why donâ€™t you take a rest, come here, Iâ€™ll sing you a song.â€</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">The ant replied: â€œThanks cicada, but Iâ€™m busy working, maybe Iâ€™ll listen when I have free time. Itâ€™s late so Iâ€™ll be moving on now!â€</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">Seeing that the cicada pursed his lips, slowly shook it head and said to himself: \"What a pitiful ant, canâ€™t even enjoy summer, why live life so miserable like that.</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">Then, the cicada once a again carried on singing, embraced the warmth of the summer sun. Time keeps passing by, autumn left and winter arrived, the colorful sunlight was no more, thereâ€™s only white snow and cold wind. Slowly trudging through the barren ground, the cicada is now trembling due to the cold and starvation.</p>\n<p class=\"p3\">\"So hungry, if only I had something to nibble on right now?\" â€“ Blown on to its hands trying to warm up, suddenly, the cicada took notice of a glowing light came from a small house by the road. Glancing through the doo, the cicada saw a familiar face: The ant! At the time, the whole ant family was gathering around the stove with warm fire and heated food placed fully on the table. Unconsciously, the cicada felt dejected, complained to itself: \"I should have stored food since summer, singing all the time canâ€™t fill a stomach!â€</p>\n[button text=\"Apply Now\"]\n\n\n[/text_box]\n\n[/ux_banner]\n[title style=\"center\" text=\"Follow on Instagram\" icon=\"icon-instagram\" margin_top=\"25px\" size=\"undefined\"]\n\n[ux_instagram_feed type=\"slider\" width=\"full-width\" columns=\"6\"]\n\n[ux_slider freescroll=\"true\" timer=\"600\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"424\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"423\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"422\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"442\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"441\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"433\"]\n\n[ux_image id=\"440\"]\n\n\n[/ux_slider]\n\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '411-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-03-19 11:50:56', '2020-03-19 11:50:56', '', 411, 'http://localhost:8888/JunNg/2020/03/19/411-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
